videos.description: Conner Frankamp finds Shaquille Morris and he throws it down for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Frankamp and Morris connect for dunk

videos.description: Markis McDuffie comes off the screen and knocks down the and-1 three.
videos.headline: Wichita State's McDuffie gets a nice 4-point play

videos.description: Landry Shamet loses his defender on a cut and Rashard Kelly finds him for the two-handed slam.

videos.description: John Thompson lll says the Shockers' ability to play unselfish basketball and having balance were their keys to victory over Houston.
videos.headline: Wichita State impresses in win against Houston
